WEBVTT

01:37.900 --> 01:41.030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 11]

01:46.610 --> 01:48.120
How could it be the towels' fault?

01:48.120 --> 01:50.039
Our hotel has been working with that

01:50.039 --> 01:52.140
towel brand and laundry for over 10 years.

01:52.140 --> 01:53.570
Never once has a guest

01:53.610 --> 01:54.990
had an allergic reaction.

01:54.990 --> 01:56.400
Then maybe the guest

01:56.430 --> 01:58.200
just has sensitive skin.

01:58.200 --> 01:58.789
So she-

01:58.789 --> 02:00.610
Then it's even less our problem.

02:00.640 --> 02:02.070
She's the one with sensitive skin.

02:02.070 --> 02:03.670
What's that got to do with us?

02:03.670 --> 02:05.180
Trying to scam the hotel?

02:05.540 --> 02:07.800
Don't even bother with people like that.

02:08.590 --> 02:09.800
The guests in that room

02:09.800 --> 02:12.170
are a few ladies
from a senior modeling team.

02:12.170 --> 02:14.030
They've stayed here for a long time.

02:14.030 --> 02:15.490
And they're quite easy to get along with.

02:15.490 --> 02:16.910
I really don't think they would-

02:16.910 --> 02:19.600
They stayed a long time, spent a lot,

02:19.620 --> 02:21.770
then right before checkout,

02:21.790 --> 02:23.360
find an excuse
to get their room comped.

02:23.360 --> 02:25.400
Trying to pull a fast one on me?

02:25.400 --> 02:26.590
No way.

02:27.110 --> 02:28.040
Go reply to them.

02:28.070 --> 02:30.030
And be firm when you do.

02:30.079 --> 02:31.350
Tell them there's absolutely

02:31.350 --> 02:33.079
nothing wrong with our towels.

02:34.430 --> 02:36.310
Mr. Feng, shouldn't we

02:36.310 --> 02:37.870
check our towels first

02:37.870 --> 02:39.079
to make sure there's no problem?

02:39.079 --> 02:40.680
Check what?

02:40.680 --> 02:41.560
Didn't I just tell you?

02:41.560 --> 02:43.190
There's no problem with the hotel!

02:43.190 --> 02:45.110
Get this straight, Xu Miyu.

02:45.180 --> 02:46.800
You are a forewoman now.

02:46.800 --> 02:47.870
You need to see things

02:47.870 --> 02:49.560
from the hotel's perspective.

02:49.560 --> 02:51.420
Otherwise, what do I need you for?

02:51.960 --> 02:53.680
But I think I...

02:55.790 --> 02:56.980
Why are you still standing here?

02:56.980 --> 02:57.980
Get to work!

02:58.200 --> 02:59.400
You're just so dense!

03:01.960 --> 03:03.030
Hello?

03:03.510 --> 03:05.140
Yes, it's me.

03:06.280 --> 03:07.280
Yes.

03:08.140 --> 03:09.140
Okay.

03:37.030 --> 03:40.079
Hello, is this Xingkang Testing Center?

03:40.079 --> 03:42.030
Yes. How can I help you?

03:42.240 --> 03:44.590
I have some towels and sheets here.

03:44.590 --> 03:46.680
I'd like to get them tested

03:46.680 --> 03:48.010
for detergent residue.

03:48.400 --> 03:49.800
We're really sorry.

03:50.240 --> 03:51.470
The hotel will definitely

03:51.470 --> 03:52.960
look into this.

03:53.360 --> 03:54.680
Once we get the results,

03:54.680 --> 03:56.680
we'll give you a satisfactory answer.

03:56.680 --> 03:58.520
When will the results come out?

03:58.520 --> 03:59.880
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

03:59.900 --> 04:02.080
Don't try to drag this out.

04:02.080 --> 04:04.560
Once this hits the news,

04:04.870 --> 04:07.310
your hotel will suffer the consequences.

04:07.310 --> 04:08.430
Don't play tricks.

04:09.370 --> 04:10.300
Go reply to them.

04:10.330 --> 04:12.240
And be firm when you do.

04:12.270 --> 04:13.610
Tell them there's absolutely

04:13.610 --> 04:15.340
nothing wrong with our towels.

04:16.329 --> 04:18.240
We won't. Rest assured.

04:18.269 --> 04:20.000
Our hotel isn't just any hotel.

04:20.019 --> 04:21.700
We will never brush it off.

04:21.950 --> 04:24.630
We just need some time

04:24.650 --> 04:26.380
to find the root of the problem.

04:26.760 --> 04:28.190
After all, nothing like this

04:28.190 --> 04:29.650
has ever happened before.

04:30.250 --> 04:31.370
Guess I'm just unlucky.

04:31.370 --> 04:32.240
Let's go home.

04:32.790 --> 04:33.900
Fang.

04:33.950 --> 04:36.590
Ms. Xu, you're a nice person,

04:36.610 --> 04:38.610
and you've taken good care of us.

04:38.640 --> 04:40.760
But you can't keep dodging

04:40.780 --> 04:42.100
the towel issue.

04:41.990 --> 04:47.770
[Recording]

04:42.310 --> 04:43.040
Yes.

04:43.060 --> 04:44.890
Fang was fine

04:44.920 --> 04:46.450
before she used your towels

04:46.510 --> 04:48.000
as a pillow for a few days,

04:48.000 --> 04:49.240
and ended up like this.

04:49.240 --> 04:49.670
Yes.

04:49.700 --> 04:51.310
If it's not your hotel's responsibility,

04:51.310 --> 04:52.630
what else is?

04:52.790 --> 04:53.720
I get it.

04:53.740 --> 04:54.940
Please rest assured.

04:55.090 --> 04:57.220
We will investigate this thoroughly.

04:57.510 --> 04:59.580
We're really sorry

04:59.640 --> 05:00.720
for the trouble.

05:01.240 --> 05:05.820
[Recording]

05:01.390 --> 05:02.680
What good is sorry?

05:02.800 --> 05:03.570
Exactly.

05:19.570 --> 05:21.010
Driver, follow that car.

05:34.020 --> 05:37.880
[Test Report]

05:39.690 --> 05:42.330
[Test Report]

05:57.000 --> 05:58.830
Mr. Ji, how can I help you?

05:58.960 --> 06:00.020
Take a look at this.

06:03.030 --> 06:04.920
[Test Report]

06:07.690 --> 06:08.580
[Test Report]

06:08.600 --> 06:10.140
[Total bacteria count: Failed]
[E. coli: Failed]

06:10.730 --> 06:11.580
This is...

06:11.610 --> 06:13.940
The test results of the hotel bath towels.

06:14.510 --> 06:16.000
So our hotel towels

06:16.000 --> 06:17.330
really are the problem.

06:17.360 --> 06:19.380
That's why the guest
had an allergic reaction.

06:19.380 --> 06:20.580
I'll go find Mr. Feng.

06:20.880 --> 06:21.710
Miyu.

06:22.640 --> 06:23.770
Take a look.

06:23.850 --> 06:25.120
You're in the video.

06:27.740 --> 06:29.480
Someone in the room
had an allergic reaction.

06:29.480 --> 06:31.240
Her neck is all swollen.

06:32.620 --> 06:33.820
A towel allergy?

06:33.850 --> 06:34.600
You must give us

06:34.600 --> 06:35.800
an explanation today.

06:35.800 --> 06:37.600
Our hotel isn't just any hotel.

06:37.600 --> 06:39.720
Nothing like this
has ever happened before.

06:39.720 --> 06:41.050
Guess I'm just unlucky.

06:45.800 --> 06:46.510
Ms. Xu.

06:46.510 --> 06:48.720
Rooms 1806 and 1817 are checking out.

06:49.250 --> 06:50.050
Got it.

06:50.470 --> 06:51.430
Go get Yin Xiang,

06:51.430 --> 06:52.600
and you two go clean up

06:52.600 --> 06:54.040
Rooms 1806 and 1817 together.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.159
She went back to the dorm.

06:55.159 --> 06:57.480
She forgot her phone and went to get it.

07:00.190 --> 07:02.250
What are you still standing here for?

07:04.000 --> 07:04.560
Ms. Xu.

07:04.560 --> 07:06.430
Rooms 1811 and 1816 are checking out.

07:06.430 --> 07:07.120
Got it.

07:09.480 --> 07:10.630
The number of guests checking out

07:10.630 --> 07:11.760
will only increase.

07:11.840 --> 07:13.170
You need to be prepared.

07:15.960 --> 07:16.730
Ke,

07:16.750 --> 07:19.210
go call Luo Qingping back
from her vacation.

07:23.520 --> 07:26.280
Everyone, gather at the Linen Room now.

07:26.980 --> 07:27.910
That won't work.

07:28.390 --> 07:29.560
No one replies

07:29.680 --> 07:31.020
to mass messages.

07:31.080 --> 07:33.409
You have to send
voice messages one by one.

07:35.060 --> 07:35.850
Stay calm.

07:36.090 --> 07:37.220
This is exactly when

07:37.220 --> 07:38.580
you can't act impulsively.

07:38.580 --> 07:39.460
Got it.

07:45.920 --> 07:47.070
Let's get out of here quickly.

07:47.070 --> 07:48.680
I'm never coming back again.

07:56.800 --> 07:57.480
Seriously.

07:57.480 --> 07:58.600
What kind of hotel is this?

07:58.600 --> 07:59.680
It's so disgusting!

07:59.680 --> 08:01.830
Exactly. How can anyone stay here?

08:02.480 --> 08:03.480
I'm so mad!

08:07.680 --> 08:09.210
I'll never stay here again!

08:09.710 --> 08:12.080
[Minhang Road]

08:18.730 --> 08:20.380
Hello everyone. My name is Peng Jie.

08:20.380 --> 08:23.270
I'm here to report serious hygiene issues

08:23.300 --> 08:25.030
with the linen at Purong Hotel.

08:25.230 --> 08:28.280
Last week, my team and I
stayed at Purong Hotel.

08:26.850 --> 08:30.040
[Name: Peng Jie]

08:28.520 --> 08:32.179
Our lead model unexpectedly
had an allergic reaction from the towels.

08:32.179 --> 08:33.610
This is my test report.

08:32.460 --> 08:34.450
[Test Report]

08:34.150 --> 08:36.240
The towels contain excessive bleach.

08:36.240 --> 08:38.330
All three bacteria tests failed.

08:45.100 --> 08:47.200
The excessive bleach incident
at Purong Hotel

08:47.200 --> 08:48.940
has drawn widespread attention today.

08:48.940 --> 08:49.920
According to reports,

08:49.920 --> 08:52.510
a guest developed an allergic reaction

08:52.510 --> 08:53.790
after using hotel towels

08:53.790 --> 08:54.870
during their stay.

08:57.800 --> 09:00.140
A single spark
can start a fire these days, huh?

09:00.140 --> 09:01.230
It's just a towel.

09:01.260 --> 09:03.860
Is it necessary
to make such a big deal out of it?

09:10.070 --> 09:12.430
Go on! Move!

09:14.970 --> 09:16.800
Just shift over a little. Problem solved.

09:16.800 --> 09:17.680
Psycho!

09:19.890 --> 09:20.880
[Wei Siyuan]
[Answer][Decline]

09:27.580 --> 09:28.910
Are you sober yet?

09:28.930 --> 09:30.200
Well, I...

09:30.480 --> 09:31.360
I'm already on my way.

09:31.360 --> 09:32.380
I'll be there soon.

09:32.380 --> 09:33.220
Um,

09:33.790 --> 09:35.240
let me handle this.

09:35.680 --> 09:36.670
Mr. Wei,

09:36.800 --> 09:38.870
I already have a solution.

09:39.030 --> 09:40.240
You better have.

09:41.420 --> 09:42.190
[Wei Siyuan
Call Ended]

10:04.710 --> 10:05.950
How many have you got?

10:05.970 --> 10:07.230
Five already.

10:07.370 --> 10:09.400
That whole row over there—all checked out.

10:09.400 --> 10:10.940
Same here.

10:11.250 --> 10:13.130
I heard the Laundry Room is full,

10:13.160 --> 10:14.440
and the linen carts can't get through.

10:14.440 --> 10:15.550
All stuck in traffic.

10:15.550 --> 10:16.600
-Really?
-At a time like this,

10:16.600 --> 10:17.550
you two are still chatting?

10:17.550 --> 10:18.150
Make way.

10:18.150 --> 10:19.720
Why? What's your problem?

10:19.720 --> 10:20.670
We've been busy since early morning.

10:20.670 --> 10:21.910
And we can't even say a word?

10:21.910 --> 10:23.340
It's not like I made the guests check out.

10:23.340 --> 10:25.100
Step back, Xiaoxue.

10:25.910 --> 10:27.240
Is no one in charge here?

10:28.060 --> 10:29.420
Sorry, my bad.

10:31.000 --> 10:32.850
Sorry, my bad.

10:35.130 --> 10:36.380
Come on, this way.

10:36.870 --> 10:37.810
Sorry.

10:43.740 --> 10:44.670
Move forward.

10:48.510 --> 10:49.700
Miyu.

10:50.120 --> 10:51.780
Is there more after this load?

10:53.180 --> 10:54.360
I don't know either.

10:54.480 --> 10:57.140
Room 1808 checking out.
Room 1807 checking out.

10:59.760 --> 11:00.690
Got it.

11:00.710 --> 11:01.700
Alright.

11:01.790 --> 11:03.220
If anyone's gonna break down,
it's not you.

11:03.220 --> 11:04.350
Stop being so whiny.

11:04.760 --> 11:06.880
I refunded my ticket home.

11:06.970 --> 11:08.920
And they charged a 20% cancellation fee.

11:08.920 --> 11:10.040
Then don't come.

11:10.060 --> 11:12.300
It's not like the executive floor
can't do without you.

11:12.300 --> 11:13.320
Go be a college student.

11:13.320 --> 11:14.580
Enough. Stop arguing.

11:14.760 --> 11:16.310
Move this cart out,

11:16.330 --> 11:18.740
then everyone head back
to the Linen Room to rest.

11:18.740 --> 11:19.540
Good work.

11:21.580 --> 11:22.680
Sorry

11:23.060 --> 11:25.190
to call you back while you're on leave.

11:26.350 --> 11:27.610
You already called me.

11:27.690 --> 11:29.050
Save the sweet talk.

11:31.120 --> 11:33.710
Well, when I came up just now,

11:33.730 --> 11:35.950
I saw that the other floors
were a total mess.

11:35.950 --> 11:38.550
Ours is at least... somewhat organized.

11:49.910 --> 11:51.710
You guys are taking a break here?

11:52.390 --> 11:55.240
There's been a lot of drama
on your executive floor lately.

11:55.240 --> 11:57.510
First, Black Card Ji came

11:57.510 --> 11:59.320
and terrified everyone.

11:59.340 --> 12:00.320
Then right after that,

12:00.320 --> 12:01.910
Mr. Duan Jr. arrived

12:01.910 --> 12:03.170
in all his glory,

12:03.210 --> 12:05.800
clearing out
he executive floor in a flash.

12:05.820 --> 12:06.940
And now look,

12:06.970 --> 12:09.300
the whole hotel is having a mass checkout.

12:09.320 --> 12:10.630
All of us other departments

12:10.630 --> 12:12.630
are stuck cleaning up your mess.

12:12.660 --> 12:13.570
Such bad luck.

12:13.840 --> 12:15.910
Well, Xiaoyan,
you can't blame me for that.

12:15.910 --> 12:17.320
I'm exhausted too.

12:17.320 --> 12:18.320
Look at me,

12:19.720 --> 12:21.270
my hands are swollen.

12:21.610 --> 12:23.450
Look at my legs, will you?

12:23.480 --> 12:26.470
I've been standing all morning.
They're like two logs by now.

12:26.470 --> 12:28.940
The bell desk is also complaining.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.320
You executive floor staff

12:30.320 --> 12:31.790
better keep a low profile now,

12:31.790 --> 12:33.320
or you might get jumped.

12:33.320 --> 12:35.910
I actually wish
someone would knock me out,

12:36.150 --> 12:37.630
so I could comfortably

12:37.630 --> 12:39.200
rest in the dorm.

12:39.230 --> 12:40.320
You have no idea—

12:40.320 --> 12:42.440
the executive floor
is covered in linens now.

12:42.440 --> 12:43.360
It's a nightmare.

12:43.360 --> 12:44.760
I don't even dare to go up.

12:45.080 --> 12:46.950
Ke? Ke, are you there?

12:46.970 --> 12:48.370
Please reply if you copy.

12:48.570 --> 12:49.650
They're calling you.

12:49.650 --> 12:51.010
Hurry up and get to work.

12:53.530 --> 12:55.750
It's fine. I'll just pretend
I didn't get it.

12:55.750 --> 12:56.910
I'll hang out with you guys a bit longer.

12:56.910 --> 12:58.630
Aren't you afraid
your forewoman will yell at you?

12:58.630 --> 13:00.320
Miyu wouldn't do that.

13:00.340 --> 13:01.340
We just give her

13:01.390 --> 13:02.870
all the work we don't want to do,

13:02.870 --> 13:04.130
and she'll do it for us.

13:04.210 --> 13:06.540
Your forewoman's that much of a pushover?

13:06.720 --> 13:07.790
Of course.

13:08.080 --> 13:10.010
She didn't earn her position.

13:10.040 --> 13:11.640
So what right does she have to manage you?

13:11.640 --> 13:12.470
True.

13:31.700 --> 13:32.470
Ms. Xu,

13:32.510 --> 13:34.370
the new laundry's
finished linens are here.

13:34.370 --> 13:36.720
Mr. Feng wants them replaced immediately.

13:36.720 --> 13:37.550
Got it.

13:38.650 --> 13:39.250
Four.

13:40.420 --> 13:42.290
Everyone, the new linens are here.

13:42.290 --> 13:44.620
Please do another round of replacements.

14:24.290 --> 14:25.770
Here, let me help you.

14:25.820 --> 14:26.640
Thank you.

14:26.670 --> 14:27.570
Careful.

14:27.670 --> 14:28.190
Okay.

14:28.240 --> 14:28.890
Okay.

14:29.440 --> 14:30.080
Sir,

14:30.150 --> 14:31.510
how did you get in here?

14:31.530 --> 14:33.800
This is the Laundry Room,
a major work area.

14:33.800 --> 14:35.460
Outsiders are not allowed in.

14:35.460 --> 14:36.190
I'm sorry.

14:36.290 --> 14:37.440
I just want to wash some clothes.

14:37.440 --> 14:38.280
I'm in a hurry to wear them.

14:38.280 --> 14:39.810
Can you do me a favor?

14:39.940 --> 14:40.750
No, no.

14:40.750 --> 14:42.600
You have to follow the process.

14:42.600 --> 14:44.460
Register at the HSKP Department first.

14:44.460 --> 14:45.790
I know the process.

14:45.880 --> 14:47.670
I've worked at Purong Hotel for years.

14:47.670 --> 14:48.850
I'm a veteran employee.

14:48.850 --> 14:50.290
Doesn't matter if you're a veteran.

14:50.290 --> 14:51.750
Our linens haven't even been

14:51.750 --> 14:52.910
sent out to wash yet.

14:52.910 --> 14:54.880
They've been piling up for half a day.

14:54.880 --> 14:57.510
I remember this place
used to be quite efficient.

14:57.510 --> 15:00.090
Why are there so many piling up now?

15:00.720 --> 15:01.670
You know how it was.

15:01.670 --> 15:04.000
Everything used to be well-organized.

15:04.000 --> 15:04.720
But now,

15:04.720 --> 15:06.500
it's a mess everywhere.

15:06.530 --> 15:08.200
It's a wonder nothing's gone wrong sooner.

15:08.200 --> 15:09.850
Didn't the director of the HSKP Department

15:09.850 --> 15:11.730
switch to a new laundry vendor?

15:11.820 --> 15:13.360
So why is it still like this?

15:13.510 --> 15:14.950
It's the same.

15:15.080 --> 15:17.240
It still follows Feng's order.

15:21.200 --> 15:23.860
The director of the HSKP Department
named Feng.

15:24.050 --> 15:24.800
Feng Kaixin.

15:27.210 --> 15:29.630
Look, these linens
haven't been replaced for years.

15:29.630 --> 15:31.820
Just bleached white over and over.

15:31.850 --> 15:33.630
How greedy is that?

15:34.040 --> 15:36.160
Treating guests like fools.

15:36.720 --> 15:37.720
It's criminal.

15:38.020 --> 15:40.550
Just thinking about it
makes me itch all over.

15:48.620 --> 15:49.580
Everyone,

15:49.610 --> 15:51.010
it's okay to take a break.

15:51.530 --> 15:52.370
Later,

15:52.860 --> 15:55.250
let's hurry up and work harder,

15:55.280 --> 15:56.670
sort these linens out,

15:56.670 --> 15:58.130
and put the new linens on first.

15:58.130 --> 15:58.890
Alright?

15:59.390 --> 16:01.320
I really can't do it anymore, Miyu.

16:01.570 --> 16:03.350
I can't even lift my arms.

16:03.390 --> 16:05.510
These are all clean linens.

16:05.840 --> 16:08.070
Who can even tell if we swap them or not?

16:08.150 --> 16:09.150
We might not,

16:09.150 --> 16:10.960
but the guests can feel the difference.

16:10.960 --> 16:12.550
Those from the new laundry factory

16:12.550 --> 16:13.870
are still safer.

16:14.070 --> 16:14.940
Ms. Xu,

16:14.990 --> 16:17.230
can you even tell which towel

16:17.250 --> 16:18.680
came from the new laundry

16:18.700 --> 16:20.390
and which from the old?

16:20.440 --> 16:21.570
The colors are the same.

16:21.570 --> 16:22.810
They feel the same.

16:22.840 --> 16:23.910
What's the difference?

16:23.910 --> 16:26.100
Jia, didn't I just tell you?

16:26.210 --> 16:28.040
We can't just focus
on the surface in service.

16:28.040 --> 16:29.540
Spare us the lectures.

16:29.560 --> 16:31.090
I just want to ask one thing.

16:31.440 --> 16:32.670
This is clearly the higher-ups' fault.

16:32.670 --> 16:34.330
Why do we have to take the fall?

16:34.590 --> 16:35.920
Is it just because we attendants

16:35.920 --> 16:37.630
at the bottom have no voice?

16:38.200 --> 16:40.530
We've been working over 10 hours already.

16:40.870 --> 16:43.330
Is this overtime
or some kind of punishment?

16:43.360 --> 16:44.120
I'm sorry.

16:44.960 --> 16:47.270
I didn't think it through.

16:48.400 --> 16:51.350
Everyone, let's push a little longer.

16:51.590 --> 16:53.870
I'll go fight for overtime pay right now.

17:00.390 --> 17:01.450
Overtime pay?

17:01.560 --> 17:03.070
How can you even ask for that?

17:03.070 --> 17:04.710
You caused this huge mess,

17:03.140 --> 17:06.990
[Purong Hotel]

17:04.730 --> 17:06.240
and you still have the nerve
to ask for money?

17:06.240 --> 17:07.440
Are you out of your mind?

17:07.440 --> 17:08.200
Mr. Feng,

17:08.660 --> 17:10.720
it's clearly stated
in the employee handbook

17:10.720 --> 17:12.599
that exceeding regular work hours

17:12.599 --> 17:13.790
must be compensated by the hour.

17:13.790 --> 17:15.349
Wh-What compensation?

17:15.380 --> 17:17.099
You drove the guests away.

17:17.119 --> 17:18.740
I should be the one
asking for compensation!

17:18.740 --> 17:20.780
The guests left
because of the linen issue,

17:20.780 --> 17:22.369
not because of us attendants.

17:22.369 --> 17:24.369
How is it not the attendants' fault?

17:24.440 --> 17:27.020
It's because you gave them bad service

17:27.050 --> 17:28.990
that they started nitpicking the hardware.

17:28.990 --> 17:30.110
If you had swapped them out more often,

17:30.110 --> 17:30.880
how could there

17:30.880 --> 17:32.070
have been an allergy issue at all?

17:32.070 --> 17:33.960
The guest's allergic to bleach.

17:33.960 --> 17:36.000
The more often we swap,
the worse the allergy gets.

17:36.000 --> 17:37.070
And regarding the linen issue,

17:37.070 --> 17:38.400
I've been keeping you updated.

17:38.400 --> 17:39.400
Stop right there.

17:39.420 --> 17:40.830
Let me tell you, Xu Miyu,

17:40.860 --> 17:42.100
don't give me that.

17:42.120 --> 17:43.750
I made you forewoman.

17:43.790 --> 17:45.780
It's not for you to manage upward on me,

17:45.780 --> 17:48.060
but to manage the people below you

17:48.090 --> 17:49.020
and manage yourself!

17:49.020 --> 17:50.140
What about our overtime pay?

17:50.140 --> 17:51.330
Still on overtime pay, huh?

17:51.330 --> 17:52.480
Do you want to quit?

17:54.450 --> 17:55.550
Anything else?

17:56.580 --> 17:57.380
Nothing.

18:11.790 --> 18:12.620
Everyone.

18:18.190 --> 18:20.280
Let's call it a day.

18:20.610 --> 18:22.300
Go back and rest.

18:23.880 --> 18:24.560
Ms. Xu,

18:25.070 --> 18:27.160
did we get our overtime pay?

18:27.640 --> 18:28.990
Clearly no chance.

18:29.770 --> 18:31.770
I knew it. Empty promises as always.

18:36.570 --> 18:38.730
Ms. Xu, I can't take the night shift.

18:39.480 --> 18:40.770
Don't. I'll take it.

19:05.830 --> 19:06.920
Earlier today,

19:06.920 --> 19:08.920
the famous Shanghai Purong Hotel

19:08.920 --> 19:10.370
was exposed by self-media

19:10.370 --> 19:12.530
for excessive bleach in its linens,

19:12.560 --> 19:14.310
causing severe allergies to guests.

19:14.310 --> 19:16.830
The incident is currently
under investigation.

19:16.540 --> 19:18.580
[Imperial Court 28, Pujiang]

19:16.850 --> 19:20.250
Relevant departments
may be involved in the investigation.

19:25.110 --> 19:25.920
Hello.

19:27.610 --> 19:28.470
Please come in.

19:33.440 --> 19:34.440
This way, please.

19:50.070 --> 19:51.040
Chairman Wei.

19:52.510 --> 19:54.380
I knew you'd come.

19:54.800 --> 19:55.980
If not tonight,

19:56.170 --> 19:57.120
then tomorrow.

19:58.640 --> 19:59.840
Purong Hotel

20:00.680 --> 20:01.550
is currently

20:01.750 --> 20:04.430
facing a critical PR crisis.

20:05.760 --> 20:08.550
I know you won't stand by and do nothing.

20:08.570 --> 20:10.250
It is indeed very difficult

20:10.400 --> 20:12.830
to achieve the condition of
turning losses into profits of over 30%

20:12.830 --> 20:13.970
within a year.

20:13.990 --> 20:16.270
But securing Kuanli's investment

20:16.430 --> 20:19.430
is a turning point for Purong.

20:21.630 --> 20:23.260
You don't want to just

20:23.280 --> 20:24.500
give Purong Hotel away.

20:24.500 --> 20:25.790
Purong

20:25.990 --> 20:27.430
can't lose this bet.

20:27.910 --> 20:30.600
I'm prepared to take drastic measures.

20:32.370 --> 20:34.380
Based on my observations recently,

20:35.190 --> 20:37.320
drastic measures might not be enough

20:37.550 --> 20:39.420
for the current Purong Hotel.

20:40.170 --> 20:42.430
We might need to make severe sacrifices.

20:43.240 --> 20:45.940
First, we must reform the system

20:45.960 --> 20:48.960
to change the hotel's mindset
from top to bottom.

20:48.990 --> 20:51.230
Then cut off corrupt collusion.

20:52.520 --> 20:54.920
By rectifying internal corruption,

20:54.990 --> 20:56.510
we must break the profit chains

20:56.510 --> 20:58.410
that severely drain the hotel's wealth.

20:58.410 --> 20:59.820
The first to go

20:59.850 --> 21:01.180
if the HSKP Department.

21:01.540 --> 21:04.100
Beyond the linen issue
making headlines these days,

21:04.100 --> 21:05.970
the toiletries in the HSKP Department

21:05.970 --> 21:07.210
also have

21:07.380 --> 21:09.580
channel and management loopholes.

21:10.070 --> 21:12.730
Of course, these are just
the surface symptoms.

21:13.550 --> 21:14.750
Once the profit chains are cut,

21:14.750 --> 21:17.400
their mutual protection network
will start to crumble.

21:17.400 --> 21:19.860
Then we sever the interpersonal collusion.

21:20.360 --> 21:21.380
Corruption is ultimately about

21:21.380 --> 21:24.240
managers stealing from their own posts.

21:24.320 --> 21:26.780
The root of the problem
lies with the people.

21:27.220 --> 21:29.460
If management itself isn't solid,

21:29.910 --> 21:32.110
Purong Hotel's disease can never be cured.

21:32.110 --> 21:33.310
My nephew

21:33.680 --> 21:36.700
just doesn't know how to run a hotel.

21:36.930 --> 21:38.460
I invited you here this time

21:38.480 --> 21:40.770
to help him pull up the weeds

21:40.800 --> 21:42.310
and clean up the backyard.

21:42.580 --> 21:45.580
We can't ruin Purong Hotel's reputation.

21:58.440 --> 22:00.150
[Total Attrition Rate]
[Analysis of Attrition Reasons]

21:58.750 --> 22:00.410
The attrition rate is so high.

22:00.470 --> 22:02.640
It's all the reporters
stirring up trouble.

22:02.640 --> 22:04.240
It wasn't a big deal at first,

22:04.260 --> 22:06.340
but some meddlers hyped it up.

22:07.060 --> 22:08.460
Since that's the case,

22:10.370 --> 22:12.770
we might as well
let nature take its course.

22:13.870 --> 22:15.700
Arrange a media briefing

22:16.040 --> 22:17.370
to appease all parties.

22:18.320 --> 22:19.930
That's a good idea.

22:20.240 --> 22:22.730
But we should plan in advance what to say

22:22.810 --> 22:24.540
and how to say it at the meeting.

22:24.640 --> 22:26.370
We can't have any more trouble.

22:28.290 --> 22:29.330
I'm here.

22:30.670 --> 22:32.230
Everything is sorted out.

22:34.050 --> 22:34.910
Zhigang.

22:39.290 --> 22:42.770
Mr. Wei, I've changed
the laundry supplier.

22:42.930 --> 22:44.520
You can trust me to handle things...

22:44.520 --> 22:46.540
What's the use of
changing the laundry supplier?

22:46.540 --> 22:47.670
I told you a long time ago

22:47.670 --> 22:49.560
to focus more on your work.

22:49.860 --> 22:50.810
And what did you do?

22:50.810 --> 22:53.290
All you know is drinking every day.

22:53.310 --> 22:54.560
Now look what you've done,

22:54.560 --> 22:55.770
causing such a huge mess.

22:55.770 --> 22:57.120
How am I supposed to
explain this to the Old Madam,

22:57.120 --> 22:59.030
and to the old folks on the board?

22:59.050 --> 23:00.140
Tell me!

23:02.070 --> 23:02.750
Well,

23:02.810 --> 23:03.700
how about this?

23:03.730 --> 23:06.300
I'll find a few guys
to warn the troublemaker

23:06.580 --> 23:08.640
and make him withdraw the complaint.

23:09.220 --> 23:11.270
You watch too many movies!

23:11.380 --> 23:13.660
Purong Hotel is such a big hotel,

23:13.690 --> 23:15.370
and you want to play gangster?

23:15.390 --> 23:17.450
Alcohol must have ruined your brain.

23:17.680 --> 23:20.480
Kaixin, just drop it.

23:24.380 --> 23:26.660
An allergic reaction
like this has never happened before.

23:26.610 --> 23:28.570
[Home] [Recommend]

23:27.470 --> 23:28.880
At this point,

23:28.910 --> 23:30.500
there's no putting it out.

23:31.720 --> 23:33.640
All we can do is steer public opinion

23:33.640 --> 23:36.850
so it doesn't blow back on us.

23:39.670 --> 23:41.130
Shift all the media attention

23:40.920 --> 23:43.160
[Home] [Recommend]

23:41.350 --> 23:43.540
onto her.

23:43.860 --> 23:46.210
After all, she is the one on camera.

23:46.310 --> 23:48.720
And the words came out of her mouth.

23:48.740 --> 23:50.500
We might as well

23:50.530 --> 23:52.560
turn this bleach incident

23:52.640 --> 23:54.400
into her personal behavior.

23:54.790 --> 23:56.900
Like being careless at work

23:57.040 --> 23:58.740
and irresponsible to the guests.

23:58.740 --> 23:59.410
Then,

23:59.850 --> 24:02.400
we will deal with her internally.

24:02.840 --> 24:05.030
Play it down and smooth it over.

24:06.810 --> 24:07.650
Too...

24:10.800 --> 24:12.730
Forewoman of the executive floor?

24:14.750 --> 24:15.980
Just promoted.

24:16.010 --> 24:16.690
Why?

24:17.020 --> 24:18.880
Does she have someone backing her?

24:18.880 --> 24:19.620
She...

24:20.100 --> 24:21.430
She works for Old Madam.

24:23.140 --> 24:24.980
You don't know my aunt.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.950
She looks kind,

24:27.220 --> 24:29.370
but she is an absolute businesswoman.

24:29.710 --> 24:30.910
She is very ruthless.

24:31.420 --> 24:33.340
The trouble is at her doorstep now.

24:33.340 --> 24:35.610
As long as you handle this matter well,

24:35.700 --> 24:37.490
she won't say anything about it.

24:37.490 --> 24:37.950
[Monday, January 6th,
7th of the 12th Lunar Month]

24:44.530 --> 24:46.460
Ji Feng went to see the chairwoman.

24:51.440 --> 24:53.890
It's just that you took
on this role in a crisis

24:53.890 --> 24:55.970
without even a proper ceremony.

24:56.710 --> 24:58.110
You flatter me, Ms. Wei.

24:59.120 --> 25:00.790
It's my honor

25:00.820 --> 25:02.610
to help Purong Hotel

25:02.640 --> 25:04.130
at such a critical moment.

25:04.160 --> 25:06.490
Your current achievements and abilities

25:06.810 --> 25:09.960
prove that I wasn't wrong about you.

25:10.350 --> 25:13.030
Being able to repay your kindness
in recognizing my talent

25:13.030 --> 25:15.350
is my opportunity and glory.

25:15.370 --> 25:19.240
Do you need me to escort you
to your new post tomorrow?

25:20.610 --> 25:22.600
The hotel is currently
at the center of public opinion.

25:22.600 --> 25:25.930
If you go, you'll just give
the reporters more to talk about.

25:26.780 --> 25:29.180
It's better if you direct things remotely.

25:31.940 --> 25:33.480
The time for the press conference is set.

25:33.480 --> 25:34.430
9 a.m. tomorrow.

25:34.460 --> 25:36.930
I'll personally oversee the venue setup.

25:37.350 --> 25:38.620
As for the Communications Department,

25:38.620 --> 25:40.640
I told them to draft
a press release first,

25:40.640 --> 25:42.560
find some influencers to post it,

25:42.850 --> 25:44.280
and stir up some buzz.

25:46.260 --> 25:47.750
[Aunt]

26:03.440 --> 26:04.070
Aunt.

26:04.100 --> 26:04.870
Siyuan.

26:05.170 --> 26:08.250
A new general manager
will take office tomorrow,

26:08.310 --> 26:09.790
to deal with this crisis.

26:10.050 --> 26:11.960
I invited him back from abroad.

26:12.270 --> 26:14.030
He is very experienced.

26:14.410 --> 26:15.540
You should know him.

26:15.550 --> 26:16.640
His name is Ji Feng.

26:17.240 --> 26:18.920
Do you remember him?

26:21.690 --> 26:24.750
[Ten years ago]

26:23.160 --> 26:23.920
Aunt,

26:23.950 --> 26:25.030
why?

26:27.320 --> 26:29.320
You promised me.

26:29.440 --> 26:32.110
You said you'd give me
the recommendation letter.

26:32.110 --> 26:34.200
Why did you go back on your word
and give it to someone else?

26:34.200 --> 26:34.960
What I told you

26:34.960 --> 26:36.490
was that I would think about it.

26:36.490 --> 26:38.450
I was almost on my knees.

26:38.480 --> 26:40.070
What else do you want me to do?

26:40.070 --> 26:41.310
Some nobody foreman

26:41.310 --> 26:42.710
just shows up out of nowhere

26:42.710 --> 26:44.230
and takes what's mine?

26:44.260 --> 26:45.530
Why is that, Aunt?

26:45.710 --> 26:46.880
You'd rather support someone

26:46.880 --> 26:48.680
who has nothing to do with you

26:48.680 --> 26:51.240
than help your own nephew!

26:52.290 --> 26:53.380
Wei Siyuan!

26:53.790 --> 26:54.790
Over the years,

26:54.810 --> 26:56.640
I have been carefully cultivating

26:56.640 --> 26:58.310
useful talents.

26:58.380 --> 27:00.900
Ji Feng is capable and ambitious.

27:00.990 --> 27:03.790
He came to me himself
for a recommendation letter.

27:03.930 --> 27:05.900
Of course I am willing to build

27:05.930 --> 27:07.390
this good relationship for Purong.

27:07.390 --> 27:09.500
Then why couldn't that person be me?

27:09.530 --> 27:11.470
Am I that useless to you?

27:11.590 --> 27:14.900
Do you really want
to learn something by going abroad?

27:14.930 --> 27:17.410
You fool around outside all day.

27:17.430 --> 27:19.970
How can I feel at ease
letting you go abroad?

27:21.680 --> 27:23.830
Hello, Siyuan?

27:25.380 --> 27:26.180
Aunt.

27:26.730 --> 27:28.450
Okay, I got it.

27:50.900 --> 27:52.510
Welcome, friends from the media.

27:52.510 --> 27:54.350
Please get your press badges first,

27:54.350 --> 27:55.590
then ahead,

27:55.590 --> 27:57.030
you will see our sign-in area.

27:57.030 --> 27:58.190
Just sign in there.

27:58.220 --> 27:59.160
If you need anything,

27:59.160 --> 28:00.160
you can come to me anytime.

28:00.160 --> 28:01.590
Yes, get your press badges here.

28:01.590 --> 28:02.350
Thank you.

28:01.630 --> 28:06.800
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

28:09.040 --> 28:12.070
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

28:14.070 --> 28:15.790
Hello, hello, hello.

28:15.470 --> 28:18.040
[Sign-in Desk]

28:18.520 --> 28:20.520
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

28:20.550 --> 28:21.830
[Sign-in Desk]

28:24.440 --> 28:26.130
Hello, everyone.

28:26.160 --> 28:28.480
Welcome to today's program.

28:26.630 --> 28:29.050
[Boyuan TV]

28:28.480 --> 28:30.740
Right now, I am inside the Purong Hotel.

28:30.760 --> 28:31.640
As you can see,

28:31.640 --> 28:33.310
we're at the sign-in desk

28:33.310 --> 28:36.040
for Purong Hotel's
linen safety media briefing.

28:40.670 --> 28:41.840
[Tuesday, January 7th,
8th Day of the 12th Lunar Month]

28:50.540 --> 28:51.640
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

29:18.780 --> 29:19.540
Mr. Wei.

29:19.950 --> 29:21.780
The press conference is about to begin.

29:21.780 --> 29:22.780
As for the speech,

29:23.000 --> 29:25.260
are you sure you don't need one prepared?

29:26.400 --> 29:27.530
No need.

29:27.720 --> 29:28.660
I know what to say.

29:28.660 --> 29:29.460
Okay.

29:30.010 --> 29:31.570
I'll go keep an eye on the venue.

29:31.570 --> 29:34.060
[Purong Hotel]

29:35.170 --> 29:36.670
[General Manager's Office]

29:42.300 --> 29:46.400
[General Manager's Office]

29:43.310 --> 29:45.060
Ji Feng? You're here.

29:45.200 --> 29:45.850
Come.

29:46.550 --> 29:47.750
Please, have a seat.

29:53.520 --> 29:55.020
You came just in time.

29:55.100 --> 29:57.100
I got a call from Aunt last night.

29:57.130 --> 29:58.750
You have no idea—it felt like

29:58.930 --> 30:01.260
a huge weight was lifted off my shoulders.

30:02.870 --> 30:04.280
It was such a relief.

30:07.370 --> 30:08.160
Ji Feng.

30:08.590 --> 30:09.960
We were in a hurry last time we met,

30:09.960 --> 30:12.240
and there were things I didn't get to say.

30:13.290 --> 30:14.570
In the past,

30:14.600 --> 30:16.670
we had some misunderstandings.

30:17.240 --> 30:19.750
Let this cup of tea be my apology to you.

30:20.030 --> 30:22.110
I hope you can let bygones be bygones

30:22.230 --> 30:23.160
and help Purong.

30:25.040 --> 30:26.570
Mr. Wei, you're too polite.

30:27.500 --> 30:29.740
I've long forgotten about the past.

30:29.980 --> 30:32.570
I came back to learn from my seniors.

30:32.750 --> 30:34.120
What seniors?

30:34.140 --> 30:36.490
How can I compare to returnees like you?

30:37.120 --> 30:38.550
What happened these past few days

30:38.550 --> 30:39.610
is a real headache.

30:39.750 --> 30:40.960
My subordinates and I

30:41.070 --> 30:42.330
can't manage it at all.

30:43.250 --> 30:46.100
Then how do you plan
to deal with it, Mr. Wei?

30:46.130 --> 30:47.200
We...

30:48.150 --> 30:48.940
Come in.

30:51.580 --> 30:54.280
Mr. Wei, the press conference is ready.

30:54.310 --> 30:55.710
Okay, I got it. You can go.

30:58.150 --> 31:00.150
Did I come at a bad time?

31:00.170 --> 31:01.170
Not at all.

31:02.520 --> 31:03.960
You came at the perfect time.

31:03.960 --> 31:05.480
How about we walk together

31:05.510 --> 31:06.790
and talk on the way?

31:06.830 --> 31:07.310
Okay.

31:07.330 --> 31:08.130
Come on.

31:13.040 --> 31:13.380
After you.

31:13.380 --> 31:13.980
After you.

31:14.210 --> 31:14.940
Please.

31:17.650 --> 31:19.590
This press conference
is making such a big scene.

31:19.590 --> 31:21.540
Everyone from the grassroots
to the leaders has to attend.

31:21.540 --> 31:22.850
What exactly is going on?

31:22.850 --> 31:23.610
I don't know.

31:23.640 --> 31:24.900
Mr. Qian spent the whole day yesterday

31:24.900 --> 31:26.250
in Mr. Wei's office.

31:26.430 --> 31:27.170
I guess the matter

31:27.170 --> 31:28.000
is not small.

31:28.400 --> 31:30.290
Why do you care if it's big or small?

31:30.290 --> 31:31.820
It's not our place to worry.

31:32.810 --> 31:34.740
Just go in and listen.

31:34.600 --> 31:37.220
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

31:34.850 --> 31:36.380
Let's take our seats first.

31:38.830 --> 31:39.550
Mr. Wei.

31:40.900 --> 31:41.900
Mr. Ji?

31:44.010 --> 31:45.590
Mr. Ji helped rescue

31:45.590 --> 31:47.950
a heart attack patient
on the executive floor.

31:47.950 --> 31:48.710
Really?

31:49.340 --> 31:50.010
Mr. Wei.

31:50.340 --> 31:51.330
The media is here.

31:51.330 --> 31:52.880
The reporters from Weekend Times
are also here,

31:52.880 --> 31:56.080
and they want to arrange
an exclusive interview with you.

31:56.290 --> 31:57.170
Ji Feng.

31:57.440 --> 31:58.930
I forgot my phone.

31:59.050 --> 31:59.910
How about this?

32:00.230 --> 32:01.450
You take Mr. Ji over there first

32:01.450 --> 32:02.850
and let him sit in my seat.

32:04.830 --> 32:06.220
Is that appropriate?

32:06.250 --> 32:08.120
That's the general manager's seat.

32:08.120 --> 32:10.000
Mr. Ji is the future general manager
of our hotel.

32:10.000 --> 32:11.800
You still think it's inappropriate?

32:11.800 --> 32:13.330
Don't just stand there, go.

32:14.060 --> 32:14.790
Understood.

32:14.960 --> 32:16.360
Mr. Ji, please follow me.

32:16.360 --> 32:16.800
Okay.

32:16.820 --> 32:18.020
I'll be there in a bit.

32:27.800 --> 32:28.600
This way.

32:35.160 --> 32:36.160
This way, please.

32:39.430 --> 32:41.160
What's he doing sitting there?

32:46.480 --> 32:49.640
Purong Hotel's media meeting
is about to begin.

32:49.640 --> 32:52.300
Friends from the press,
please take your seats.

32:54.050 --> 32:55.310
Here to watch the show?

32:57.290 --> 32:58.570
You got a good seat.

32:59.250 --> 33:00.390
Why are you here?

33:00.640 --> 33:03.420
I am the future chairman
of Purong Hotel.

33:03.480 --> 33:06.410
How could I not come
when something this big happens?

33:06.710 --> 33:09.230
Respected leaders, guests,

33:09.250 --> 33:11.010
and friends from the media,

33:11.040 --> 33:12.210
good morning.

33:12.310 --> 33:14.570
It's a great honor
to have this opportunity

33:14.570 --> 33:15.400
to gather with you all

33:15.400 --> 33:18.030
at Purong Hotel's media exchange meeting.

33:18.240 --> 33:19.250
Today,

33:19.350 --> 33:20.030
we will

33:20.030 --> 33:21.920
give a sincere response

33:21.920 --> 33:23.030
regarding the bleach incident

33:23.030 --> 33:25.400
at Purong Hotel a few days ago.

33:25.420 --> 33:26.870
A sincere response?

33:27.330 --> 33:29.310
That old fox Wei Siyuan is absent again.

33:29.310 --> 33:31.420
I wonder which fearless person

33:31.440 --> 33:33.400
will be brought out to do
the damage control this time.

33:33.400 --> 33:35.160
Now, let's welcome

33:35.290 --> 33:37.550
the new general manager of Purong Hotel,

33:37.640 --> 33:40.000
Mr. Ji Feng, to answer your questions.

33:41.520 --> 33:42.780
Who is Ji Feng?

33:43.680 --> 33:45.180
When did our hotel get
a new general manager?

33:45.180 --> 33:46.250
Yeah.

33:47.660 --> 33:48.590
Mr. Ji.

33:49.430 --> 33:50.120
Please.

34:23.190 --> 34:24.710
Good morning, everyone.

34:25.050 --> 34:27.650
I'm the new general manager
of Purong Hotel,

34:28.050 --> 34:29.080
Ji Feng.

34:32.120 --> 34:34.040
I'll keep this brief.

34:34.170 --> 34:35.460
Regarding the incident

34:35.460 --> 34:37.320
where excess bleach in the linens

34:37.370 --> 34:38.620
of the HSKP Department

34:38.620 --> 34:40.679
caused skin allergies in our guests,

34:41.010 --> 34:43.340
after investigations by various parties,

34:43.340 --> 34:46.870
it has been determined to be
a major internal error of the hotel.

34:50.370 --> 34:53.429
Purong Hotel will
take full responsibility.

34:53.460 --> 34:54.580
Please rest assured.

34:54.580 --> 34:56.060
Bring Xu Miyu here.

34:56.380 --> 34:57.320
Hurry up.

34:58.400 --> 35:00.080
Why did the new
general manager admit to it?

35:00.080 --> 35:01.570
What is he trying to do?

35:07.150 --> 35:08.030
Ms. Xu.

35:08.970 --> 35:09.740
Mr. Wu.

35:09.770 --> 35:11.170
Come with me for a moment.

35:12.360 --> 35:13.470
What is it?

35:14.590 --> 35:15.550
I'm sorry

35:15.990 --> 35:17.880
to meet you for the first time
in this way today.

35:17.070 --> 35:20.620
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

35:18.190 --> 35:19.960
Regarding Purong's
internal issues this time,

35:19.960 --> 35:21.490
I will never tolerate them.

35:21.740 --> 35:22.660
Here,

35:23.470 --> 35:24.670
I promise to all of you

35:25.000 --> 35:28.120
and the consumers in front of the camera

35:28.150 --> 35:29.100
Purong Hotel

35:29.170 --> 35:30.460
will definitely replace

35:30.460 --> 35:32.360
the problematic linen as soon as possible,

35:32.360 --> 35:34.340
thoroughly investigate
the cause of the accident,

35:34.340 --> 35:35.560
and welcome everyone's stay

35:35.560 --> 35:38.420
with a brand new look
in the shortest possible time.

35:40.390 --> 35:41.160
Go in.

35:43.800 --> 35:44.620
It's her.

35:44.640 --> 35:46.190
She is the person in the video.

35:46.190 --> 35:47.400
That's her.

35:47.400 --> 35:48.230
Yes, it's her.

35:48.230 --> 35:49.490
She's that attendant.

35:50.030 --> 35:51.760
Hello, hello.

35:51.760 --> 35:52.760
Hello.

35:52.760 --> 35:54.150
Excuse me.

35:54.150 --> 35:55.400
Did you run any tests

35:55.400 --> 35:56.360
before claiming there was no problem...

35:56.360 --> 35:58.840
-with the towels?
- What was the situation when the guest fell ill?

35:58.840 --> 35:59.920
Do you ever feel any guilt

35:59.920 --> 36:00.880
when you brushed off the guests?

36:00.880 --> 36:01.800
What's your relationship with

36:01.800 --> 36:02.760
the linen service company?

36:02.760 --> 36:04.760
-Did you profit from it?
-Who asked you to do this?

36:04.760 --> 36:05.920
Did someone else support you?

36:05.920 --> 36:07.480
Did the hotel support you?

36:07.480 --> 36:08.340
Please tell us.

36:21.060 --> 36:22.080
Miss.

36:22.510 --> 36:24.710
You don't have to answer any questions.

36:28.850 --> 36:30.570
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

36:43.440 --> 36:44.770
Friends from the media,

36:45.550 --> 36:47.960
I'm the only spokesperson
appointed by Purong Hotel

36:47.960 --> 36:49.480
regarding this incident.

36:49.690 --> 36:50.870
I will answer

36:50.900 --> 36:52.820
all your questions.

36:53.670 --> 36:55.490
Please return to your seats. Thank you.

36:55.490 --> 36:56.820
Thank you for your time.

37:14.760 --> 37:15.800
Excessive bleach

37:15.800 --> 37:18.030
is essentially not a service issue,

37:18.200 --> 37:21.110
but an oversight in executive management.

37:23.700 --> 37:25.710
As for how we will handle this matter,

37:25.710 --> 37:27.290
within 48 hours,

37:27.360 --> 37:28.940
I will give you a proper answer.

37:28.940 --> 37:30.230
Mr. Ji, may I ask

37:30.290 --> 37:31.510
if the excessive use of bleach

37:31.510 --> 37:33.510
is already a tacitly accepted fact

37:33.510 --> 37:34.760
within Purong Hotel?

37:35.360 --> 37:38.290
How long has this been
tacitly accepted internally?

37:38.960 --> 37:40.550
That is a very good question.

37:40.550 --> 37:41.980
What you're asking is exactly

37:41.980 --> 37:43.640
what we'll investigate next.

38:06.670 --> 38:08.630
Well played, Mr. Ji.

38:09.260 --> 38:10.550
You kept it from me for so long.

38:10.550 --> 38:12.300
You clearly didn't see me as a friend.

38:12.300 --> 38:13.920
You misunderstood, Mr. Duan.

38:13.920 --> 38:14.840
It was an emergency.

38:14.840 --> 38:17.070
I was forced into it.

38:17.240 --> 38:18.550
You saw it just now.

38:18.630 --> 38:20.000
I had no choice.

38:21.110 --> 38:23.440
I offered you an olive branch,
but you refused.

38:23.440 --> 38:25.440
And now you're standing against me.

38:25.440 --> 38:27.060
Whatever Wei Wanjun is paying you,

38:27.060 --> 38:28.430
I'll double it.

38:29.810 --> 38:31.980
I'm flattered you think
so highly of me, Mr. Duan.

38:31.980 --> 38:34.550
Then all the more reason
for me to prove myself first

38:34.550 --> 38:37.320
before I discuss my worth with you.

38:39.690 --> 38:40.520
Thanks.

38:50.550 --> 38:53.550
You just want to beat me.

38:54.910 --> 38:55.870
In your dreams.

39:04.840 --> 39:05.710
Ji Feng.

39:07.360 --> 39:09.180
I should address you
as General Manager now.

39:09.180 --> 39:10.570
Why are you standing here?

39:10.570 --> 39:11.540
I...

39:11.850 --> 39:12.830
I forgot to tell you,

39:12.830 --> 39:14.580
I vacated my office for you.

39:14.610 --> 39:15.490
Wait a moment.

39:15.710 --> 39:16.710
Wu.

39:17.760 --> 39:18.430
Mr. Wei.

39:18.450 --> 39:19.930
Mr. Ji is here.
Get the keys and open the door.

39:19.930 --> 39:20.680
Okay.

39:24.220 --> 39:25.090
Mr. Ji,

39:25.920 --> 39:28.040
you're the person Purong Hotel

39:28.060 --> 39:29.260
needs most right now.

39:29.760 --> 39:31.620
To be honest, I thought this would

39:31.840 --> 39:33.310
take a long time, but you're

39:33.310 --> 39:34.980
planning to move fast.

39:35.100 --> 39:37.510
Solving such a thorny crisis in 48 hours,

39:37.530 --> 39:39.300
it's like a miracle.

39:39.640 --> 39:41.280
We're all waiting to see.

39:41.300 --> 39:42.830
Do you have any ideas, Mr. Wei?

39:42.830 --> 39:44.570
What ideas could I have?

39:44.950 --> 39:46.790
I'm completely overwhelmed.

39:46.850 --> 39:47.890
It's a huge mess.

39:47.920 --> 39:49.780
My brain isn't working properly.

39:49.840 --> 39:50.670
But look,

39:50.350 --> 39:52.070
[General Manager's Office]

39:50.670 --> 39:52.360
whatever resources you need,

39:52.670 --> 39:53.480
feel free to use them.

39:53.480 --> 39:53.860
Okay.

39:54.030 --> 39:54.710
Also,

39:54.930 --> 39:56.580
I'm your soldier now.

39:56.670 --> 39:58.330
I'm at your disposal anytime.

39:59.440 --> 40:00.400
Mr. Ji, please.

40:01.690 --> 40:03.150
Mr. Wei, this is...

40:04.090 --> 40:04.940
Secretary Wu.

40:05.440 --> 40:06.760
From now on, he's your secretary.

40:06.760 --> 40:07.440
Feel free to use him.

40:07.440 --> 40:07.960
Okay.

40:08.320 --> 40:11.030
Then please inform everyone, Secretary Wu,

40:11.030 --> 40:14.360
that there will be a full
management team meeting in an hour.

40:15.760 --> 40:17.160
Why are you looking at me?

40:17.320 --> 40:19.320
Mr. Ji told you to inform them, so go.

40:20.590 --> 40:21.710
Okay, Mr. Ji.

40:27.150 --> 40:28.350
Thank you for your support, Mr. Wei.

40:28.220 --> 40:30.250
[General Manager's Office]

40:28.550 --> 40:29.990
Of course.

40:30.660 --> 40:32.950
Do you want me to show you around?

40:36.110 --> 40:36.630
No need.

40:37.070 --> 40:38.790
I'll go change.

40:38.830 --> 40:39.630
See you later

40:39.660 --> 40:40.790
in the meeting room.

40:41.280 --> 40:42.150
Okay.

40:46.780 --> 40:52.650
[General Manager's Office]

40:47.650 --> 40:48.810
Ungrateful.
